	<summary>Simple 3D step-based game, like a 3D Pac-Man</summary>
	<icon type="stock">com.github.esotericpig.EkoScape</icon>
	<!-- <icon type="cached">com.github.esotericpig.EkoScape.png</icon> -->
	<description>
		<p>
		Simple 3D step-based game, like a 3D Pac-Man. Made in C++, SDL2, and legacy OpenGL 2.0.
		The <em>assets</em> folder should have been provided with this game, and in it,
		you can edit the map files in <em>assets/maps/</em> or make your own!
		<em>Enjoy!</em>
		</p>
	</description>

